docs.text: Welcome to Test Biometric This tool has been created in order to simplify and speed up the testing process of the verbio biometrics API. Commands ./biometric_reports_generator.sh addfile_[dir-name] - Test addfile. ./biometric_reports_generator.sh jsongenerator - Json generator. ./biometric_reports_generator.sh verify_[dir-name] - Test verify. Runtime environment ❯ cd addfile . ├── Audio2009.wav ├── Audio2010.wav └── json_template.txt # Modified template for test addfile ❯ cd jsongenerator . ├── Audio2001.wav ├── Audio2002.wav └── json_template.txt # Modified template for test verify ❯ . └── report-24-02-2021.csv # Results report output
